channel.description:
Finding Coords Is Simple
Step1: Open Up Your Server
Step 2: Enter your Username and Password Then Hit Log In
Step 3: Once In-Game type ::mypos
You Should See Something like this
[IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/6xxit2.jpg[/img]
Simple As That!
